-----------------------------------------------
Create a CPC master tape from your game binary
-----------------------------------------------
This is a Win32/64 executable. It will also work with WINE under Linux, 
IT WON'T WORK IN DOS. 

A CDT tape image is the Amstrad CPC equivalent to the TZX file format. 
Have the compiled binary in the same directory as this executable and 
then enter the following: 

2cdt -n -r loaderstring YOUR.BIN imageoutname.cdt
